title: Gary Janetti
description: Casey and Danielle have writer/hilarious instagrammer/housewife lover Gary Janetti back in their loving arms to talk Teresa's and Casey's acceptable anger, "Seeking Arrangements" and why Shannon is/is not the best housewife of all time. Plus Gary recounts his own time on a reality show and how two people are not enough to make a good scene!
